Class BinaryTree.BinaryTreeNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • BinaryTree.BinaryTreeNode
  • Enclosing class:
    BinaryTree<K extends java.lang.Number & java.lang.Comparable<K>,E>

    public class BinaryTree.BinaryTreeNode
extends java.lang.Object
    This class acts as the nodes for the BinaryTree. Each node has a key and element, as well as a pointer as to which node, or null, is to it's left or right.
